| Contract Management | Contract lifecycle | 31+ active contracts: seller, buyer, qty, amount, exported/remaining, payment status. | Shohrat, Gadam |
| Gapy Satysh Portal | External portal | Simple forms for document submission. Easy interface. GPS list upload. Document receipt. | Gapy Satysh users |
